        "setup": "In the [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials), create or select a project, enable Cloud Translation, then create an API key under **APIs & Services → Credentials**. Google’s auth docs note API keys are only usable with APIs that accept them; the Cloud Translation v2 discovery document says the `key` query parameter is required unless you provide an OAuth 2.0 token.",
